      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, never smoked in, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a total dream and is in truly incredible shape inside and out. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I'm ready to pass it on to someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and show you around this beauty!",
