    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with a fully serviced dual-VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe ensuring structural rigidity. Every bushing and damper remains within factory tolerances, preserving the legendary chassis balance and communicative steering rack. Finished in a pristine state with an immaculate undercarriage and a limited-slip differential that locks with surgical precision, this is the definitive driver's car for the serious collector.",
