      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to a cabin that remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original factory scent is still present. Every tactile surface\u2014from the steering wheel stitching to the switchgear\u2014feels crisp and unused. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a whisper-quiet idle and seamless gear transitions. It comes with a complete, chronological service portfolio documented by certified specialists. This is a collector-grade specimen that satisfies the most exacting standards of excellence.",
